{"tid":666717,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【now記者北京採訪被帶走】梁君彥拒批休會辯論：不符對公眾迫切重要規定","createTime":"2018-05-16T06:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T06:39:15.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b396a348be21e5762b5907230b4d1fba0b49f195","tid":666717,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:20:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180516/s00001/1526450714119\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180516%2Fs00001%2F1526450714119&d=71H6aUdLW1dRq8EZX0xA2Rxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=9169611d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180516%2Fs00001%2F1526450714119&h=8aba1b7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180516/s00001/1526450714119</a><br />\n<br />\nnow新聞攝影師今早在北京採訪時，被多名警員按壓在地，並鎖上手扣押上警車，過程中手部受傷、額頭出血。議員許智峯在立法會大會提岀休會辯論事件。不過立法會主席梁君彥不批准動議，並指「有關事宜不符合議事規則第16(2)條所指『對公眾之言有迫切重要性』，因為議員即使不在今次會議辯論，亦不會失去表達意見的機會」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n梁君彥表示，明白議員非常關注本港有記者在內地採訪時被帶走一事，以及採訪自由重要性，但因為有關事宜不符合議事規則第16(2)條，故不批准。<br />\n<br />\n許智峯聞言向梁君彥提問：「現時仍有記者在北京採訪維權律師一事，他們的人身安全是否不是迫切重要性？」梁君彥明言他已裁決，且該問題不是規程問題，強調「我的裁決不容辯論」。<br />\n<br />\n議員毛孟靜追問，梁君彥是否已經裁定有關議題不迫切及不重要。梁君彥解釋：「若你留心聽，我只是說這事對公眾而言有迫切性，但即使不在今次會議討論，亦不會失去表達意見的機會」。"},{"pid":"2c11ef058ab0be3da60bbe070bde52e56fd224b7","tid":666717,"uid":16468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:24:28.000Z","msg":"我的裁決不容辯論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾時到法官講呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d66f2424a43f72cb3ef42a92dca1028dd6212cc","tid":666717,"uid":32588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:25:11.000Z","msg":"又係呢條大口狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d10af2a6208c1c38cf0b2548d0f47395db54cfc","tid":666717,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:39:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}